when a target node is in 'Push' Mode.\n\n```PowerShell\nUpdate-DscConfiguration     [[-ComputerName] <string[]>] \n                            [-Wait]\n                            [-Force] \n                            [-JobName <string>] \n                            [-Credential<pscredential>] \n                            [-ThrottleLimit <int>] \n                            [-WhatIf] \n                            [-Confirm] \n                            [<CommonParameters>]\n\nUpdate-DscConfiguration     -CimSession <CimSession[]> \n                            [-Wait] \n                            [-Force] \n                            [-JobName <string>] \n                            [-ThrottleLimit <int>]\n                            [-WhatIf] \n                            [-Confirm] \n                            [<CommonParameters>]\n```"}